# Skill Router

Match user intent against triggers; load **one** skill on demand. Don't pre-load.

{{SKILL_ROUTER}}

**Priority:** explicit `/slash` invocation wins. Else first-match wins. Else, no skill load.

The per-route `.cursor/rules/route-<id>.mdc` files carry the same routing
intent, scoped to make each route discoverable on its own. This file is the
consolidated table.
